            p.m-1 Planning to shop in Japan?  Name it, well find it and ship it to you.
            p.m-1 For online shoppers, with prior arrangements, fill in our address when you check out of your Japanese online store. The product will be delivered to us and we shall export it to you by either air or sea freight. 
